ng feedback on the % of the original six selected books that were by women authors, a continuous measure of the number of books initially selected that were by women authors, and an interaction between these two terms. Standard errors reported in parentheses are estimated robustly using HC3. +p<0.1;*p<0.05;**p<0.01;***p<0.001.
